{"tid":207528,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"(影片) 【舒淇賣麵】椒麻葱油拌麵攻港 網購貴過台灣買","createTime":"2017-04-19T02:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-21T01:36:36.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c5b4b3958209837b10afd04ca361137b742f0855","tid":207528,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T02:50:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.gomaji.com/products/68/149068/149068_1_1_r.jpg?1483583662\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.gomaji.com%2Fproducts%2F68%2F149068%2F149068_1_1_r.jpg%3F1483583662&h=47072682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n舒淇的instagram，最近常見她推介一包叫Kiki的拌麵。原來是她與好友陶晶瑩、藍心湄合資的餐廳Kiki restaurant的出品。她們的拌麵以高品質見稱，標榜選用台南馳名，不含防腐劑的手工日曬麵，和自家調配的醬汁，以往只能在台灣的Kiki餐廳買得到，更經常斷貨。<br />\n但最近她們在香港開設網店，每包$68有六個麵，價錢雖比台灣網店貴約$12，但只要在網上下單，三個工作天內就可以送貨。口味和台灣買到的一樣，分別是葱油拌麵和以自家調製的花椒粉做的椒麻拌麵。一份有六包麵，麵和醬料個別包裝，一打開麵條，麵粉香撲鼻而來，用水煮約三分鐘即可以食。究竟好不好食，即睇試食的同事講講。<br />\n不過要注意，價錢未包運費，運費由速遞公司收取，記者買了兩款口味，選擇在將軍澳工業邨收貨，運費就要$58，圍起每一個麵要$16。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170419/56580605\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170419%2F56580605&d=%2FOWxXeQsMLcQIgbDBmmt7gEk2Noh57F05xbgvjQdsX8%3D&h=9afcddae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fsupplement%2F20170419%2F56580605&h=f3444b58\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/supplement/20170419/56580605</a>"},{"pid":"5abfece2ed916e7ddc15d6634387b9424e7419b6","tid":207528,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T03:18:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a75afe56c4e7afe95aeb532b730775cf450bd432","tid":207528,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-19T05:54:13.000Z","msg":"窮撚只食喜達,是否悲哀?<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26385c74f5122f206ee